    <div class="text-area">
      <div class="slide-tag">Zooming into <strong>India</strong></div>
      <div class="slide-headline light">Street vending is essential urban work, largely without legal protection.</div>
      <div class="ornament"></div>
      <ul style="list-style:none; padding:0; margin:0; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:1.2vmin;">
        <li style="display:flex; gap:1vmin; align-items:flex-start;">
          <span style="color:var(--ochre); font-size:clamp(0.8rem,1vw,1rem); line-height:1.6; flex-shrink:0;">—</span>
          <span class="slide-body light" style="font-size:clamp(0.8rem,1.1vw,1.1rem);">Street vendors sell fresh produce, cooked food and everyday goods in public spaces they have no legal right to occupy</span>
        </li>
        <li style="display:flex; gap:1vmin; align-items:flex-start;">
          <span style="color:var(--ochre); font-size:clamp(0.8rem,1vw,1rem); line-height:1.6; flex-shrink:0;">—</span>
          <span class="slide-body light" style="font-size:clamp(0.8rem,1.1vw,1.1rem);">They serve millions of households daily, providing convenience and cheaper alternatives</span>
        </li>
        <li style="display:flex; gap:1vmin; align-items:flex-start;">
          <span style="color:var(--ochre); font-size:clamp(0.8rem,1vw,1rem); line-height:1.6; flex-shrink:0;">—</span>
          <span class="slide-body light" style="font-size:clamp(0.8rem,1.1vw,1.1rem);">Most lack basic infrastructure, stable tenure, and awareness of the rights the law affords them</span>
        </li>
        <li style="display:flex; gap:1vmin; align-items:flex-start;">
          <span style="color:var(--ochre); font-size:clamp(0.8rem,1vw,1rem); line-height:1.6; flex-shrink:0;">—</span>
          <span class="slide-body light" style="font-size:clamp(0.8rem,1.1vw,1.1rem);">Our research focuses on Patna, Bihar, to understand how this sector works and what it costs those within it</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

